videos.description: Angel Delgado scores two with a putback dunk off a missed 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Delgado scores a putback slam for Seton Hall

videos.description: Pat NcNamara hits a three pointer to give FDU the lead assisted by Jahlil Jenkins.
videos.headline: McNamara's transition three ball give FDU the lead

videos.description: Noah Morgan hits a corner 3-pointer in his first shot of the game to draw Fairleigh Dickinson within 11.
videos.headline: Morgan nails a 3 to draw FDU closer

videos.description: Khadeen Carrington goes the lenght of the floor and scores with a left-hand layup to extend the lead for the Pirates.
videos.headline: Carrington goes coast-to-coast for Seton Hall layup

videos.description: Michael Nzei recipient of good ball movement and scores a right-hand layup for the Pirates.
videos.headline: Nzei with nifty moves for a layup for the Hall

videos.description: Darnell Edge scores a right-handed layup while getting fouled in the second half.
videos.headline: Edge connects on and-1 for Fairleigh Dickinson
